{"data":{"wordpressPost":{"title":"Ampersand","content":"<html><head></head><body><p>This is a little illustration I made for a Shopify Design Challenge. Yesterday&#x2019;s challenge was to create an ampersand. I created this using Illustrator in about an hour, so there are some sloppy parts (the spit drops and the bones in particular). </p>\n<p><a href=\"/static/769c65172482b30715d1d7b987d5afaf/1b500/amperbleghhh.png\"><span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 650px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 107.32394366197184%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url(&apos;data:image/png;base64,&apos;); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n    <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image alignnone size-large wp-image-2170\" style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;box-shadow:inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\" alt=\"amperbleghhh\" title=\"amperbleghhh\" src=\"/static/769c65172482b30715d1d7b987d5afaf/dbb61/amperbleghhh.png\" srcset=\"/static/769c65172482b30715d1d7b987d5afaf/19bd1/amperbleghhh.png 163w,\n/static/769c65172482b30715d1d7b987d5afaf/d3bcb/amperbleghhh.png 325w,\n/static/769c65172482b30715d1d7b987d5afaf/dbb61/amperbleghhh.png 650w,\n/static/769c65172482b30715d1d7b987d5afaf/6b691/amperbleghhh.png 975w,\n/static/769c65172482b30715d1d7b987d5afaf/1b500/amperbleghhh.png 1065w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 650px) 100vw, 650px\">\n  </span></a></p>\n<div class=\"sub\">Amperbleghhhh</div>\n<p><!--more--></p>\n<p>Here is my initial sketch:</p>\n<p><a href=\"/static/6712ad3a5ff19c5d35df250c4fc72d3c/e2288/ampersand_sketch.jpg\"><span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 640px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 114.53125%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url(&apos;data:image/jpeg;base64,&apos;); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n    <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image alignnone size-full wp-image-2171\" style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;box-shadow:inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\" alt=\"ampersand sketch\" title=\"ampersand_sketch\" src=\"/static/6712ad3a5ff19c5d35df250c4fc72d3c/e2288/ampersand_sketch.jpg\" srcset=\"/static/6712ad3a5ff19c5d35df250c4fc72d3c/aca85/ampersand_sketch.jpg 163w,\n/static/6712ad3a5ff19c5d35df250c4fc72d3c/0954f/ampersand_sketch.jpg 325w,\n/static/6712ad3a5ff19c5d35df250c4fc72d3c/e2288/ampersand_sketch.jpg 640w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\">\n  </span></a></p>\n<p>I can&#x2019;t stress how helpful <a href=\"http://twitter.com/#!/Vonster\">@Vonster</a>&#x2018;s book, Vector Basic Training has been when working in Illustrator. I whipped this illustration up much quicker than I would have and the curves a much, much smoother and consistent. If you use the Pen tool a lot, I highly recommend reading <a href=\"http://www.vonglitschka.com/2010/12/24/vector-basic-training-book/\">Vector Basic Training</a>.</p>\n</body></html>"}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"slug":"ampersand"}}